  <version>1.1</version>
  <description>
<![CDATA[
Module to create Image or Content Slideshows.<br/>How-to: Create a folder vikslider in images/ and upload every image you wish to use in that folder. In case you want to make a slideshow of contents, create a file .html with the code or just text you want to view for each content to include in the slideshow. Put all these files into the same folder images/vikslider/
]]>
</description>
 
  <files>
    <filename module="mod_vikslider">mod_vikslider.php</filename>
    <filename>mod_vikslider.xml</filename>
    <filename>mod_vikslider.css</filename>
    <filename>index.html</filename>
    <filename>src/index.html</filename>
    <filename>src/jquery.js</filename>
    <filename>src/effects.js</filename>
    <filename>src/left.png</filename>
    <filename>src/right.png</filename>
  </files>
 
  <languages>
    <language tag="en-GB">language/en-GB/en-GB.mod_vikslider.ini</language>
